				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I have always used my ranger for plat farming, so I don't know how this will transfer to mages.  I have made several hundred k by farming tradeskill items and selling in the bazaar.  Here are my favorites:
<br />

<br />
Acrylia caverns:  Pick a room, rarely camped, and farm as much acrylia as you can.  My server, about 1.5k an hour
<br />

<br />
Dawnshroud Peaks: On my server this place is unreal.  Flawless hides sell FAST at 400pp per.  I can make 2.5k an hour plinking the hoppers.  Best part is, if someone tries lowering the price, you can either buy him out and keep the price up, or spawn the gorangas, as most people are too lazy to spend the time bringing the hoppers back up.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
