				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">This is just a note on the Rockhopper hides, since hoppers can be a fairly dangerous camp and are usually taken. You can go there, but there's an easier place: Shadeweaver's Thicket!
<br />

<br />
Shadeweaver's (Vah Shir newb zone) has an abundance of hoppers that drop all qualities of hides, and they rarely go higher than level 10. Any pet that can survive a minute in Paludal can spank them for fast cash! The best part is, there are so many roamers that are all over the zone... and the newbs only stay near the guards because hoppers can hit pretty hard for their weak lil' level. It doesn't matter what server you're on whether it be an old one like Bertoxxulous or a supercrowded (and superinflated) one like Morden Rasp. Nobody ever touches the level 10 hoppers far away from the guards in SWT.
<br />

<br />
This is how you get a couple thousand plat at level 15, as well as some minimal experience... of course, the profit grows larger when you kill them ever faster, and a DPoC'd Ward of Xegony only needs to stun-swat them and you're stripping that hide off like yesterday's wallpaper.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=706123" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Medya Wyvernslayer</a>
<br />
Othokent vorastrix aesthyr kuru kosj darastrix, shar korth sjerit leirith.
<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">Smart magician woman slays small dragons; but danger yet near.</span></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
